N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 206.16 - Personnel changes in business entity licensee

State Regulations
A business entity licensee shall notify the Commission
immediately of any changes to the officers, responsible parties or directors
listed in the entity's license application by filing an amendment thereto with
the Commission. Notes
